{
  "texts": [
    "For each case, we obtained the output from ChatGPT (Step 1: Generate answer without choices).",
    "Then we input the answer choices and asked ChatGPT to choose one of them (Step 2: Generate answer with choices).",
    "Two author physicians confirmed whether the answer generated by ChatGPT matched the ground truth.",
    "If there was a discrepancy, a third author physician made the decision.",
    "We introduced this process of confirmation in case the difference was purely linguistic."
  ]
}